{"tid":1845352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"李克強赴武漢 「封城」後首位支那最高決策官員","createTime":"2020-01-27T06:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T04:35:25.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cb4a685e1a6d83b1f9674eb725ed2d4f15ec3ebc","tid":1845352,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"隨著「武漢肺炎」疫情升溫，疫情重災區武漢市於1月23日上午10時「封城」，身兼「中共中央應對新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情工作領導小組」組長的大陸總理李克強，今天到武漢探望第一線醫護人員，是武漢「封城」以來到當地的中共最高決策層級官員。<br />\n <br />\n大陸官媒上午就李克強赴武漢發出簡短的報導，據「中國政府網」，1月27日農曆正月初三，受中共總書記習近平委託，中共中央政治局常委、大陸國務院總理、中共中央應對新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情工作領導小組組長李克強來到武漢，考察指導疫情防控工作，看望慰問患者和奮戰在一線的醫護人員。"},{"pid":"42cf9ffeaaf716f5562b4269e35ca22f0385f82d","tid":1845352,"uid":32511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wYT3gN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYT3gN0.jpg&h=7a50484b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑仔強算係咁，反觀維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52deb21fac92202ebee25592e37d283665557111","tid":1845352,"uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"原來當年黑仔強主政河南出左愛滋村<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f1cc90e834ddd79a1b717d59606a5579d06459","tid":1845352,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52deb21fac92202ebee25592e37d283665557111","tid":1845352,"uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"原來當年黑仔強主政河南出左愛滋村<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/